<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Fountain_pen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.vintagepens.com/early_cartridge_pens.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.vintagepens.com/early_cartridge_pens.shtml" rel="nofollow">Early Cartridge Pens</a> (Article about the very first cartridge pens, from the early 20th century)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.penhero.com/PenGalleryMain.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.penhero.com/PenGalleryMain.htm" rel="nofollow">PenHero.com</a> (Many illustrated articles and reviews on modern and vintage pens)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pendemonium.com/ink_facts.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.pendemonium.com/ink_facts.htm" rel="nofollow">Pendemonium: Ink Facts</a> (Reviews on inks and list of cartridge type used by different fountain pens.)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.marcuslink.com/pens" class="external text" title="http://www.marcuslink.com/pens" rel="nofollow">Glenn's Pen Page</a> (Reviews of pen shops and fountain pen inks)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.penexchange.de/english/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.penexchange.de/english/index.html" rel="nofollow">Penexchange</a> (Information and forum for pen collectors, hosted by <a href="/wiki/Pelikan" title="Pelikan">Pelikan</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.rickconner.net/penspotters/" class="external text" title="http://www.rickconner.net/penspotters/" rel="nofollow">Penspotters</a> (Information site about fountain pens)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.richardspens.com/ref.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.richardspens.com/ref.htm" rel="nofollow">Richard's Pens</a> (Information from a fountain pen restorer)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ruettinger-web.de/e-index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ruettinger-web.de/e-index.html" rel="nofollow">Infos for Pelikan collectors</a> (Information site about Pelikan fountain pens)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.stylophilesonline.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.stylophilesonline.com/" rel="nofollow">Stylophiles on-line magazine</a> (On-line magazine devoted to fountain pen enthusiasts and aficionados.)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.parkerpens.net" class="external text" title="http://www.parkerpens.net" rel="nofollow">Parkerpens.net</a> (Unofficial fan-site with plenty of information about vintage Parker pens.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.richardink.com" class="external text" title="http://www.richardink.com" rel="nofollow">Richardink.com</a> (Fountain pen artisan and expert Richard Lee Merritt's pen blog.)</li>
</ul>
